title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 79-4.13 - Moral character for polysomnographic technologist authorization
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 79-4.13 - Moral character for polysomnographic technologist authorization

State Regulations

Applicants shall be of good moral character, as
determined by the department. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8
§§
79-4.13

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
